<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 xiàng shén yǎng liǎn zài yè gèng de shí hòu, xiàng shén yǎng liǎn zài tiān wèi liàng de shí hòu,
 děng hòu yé hé huá bì cóng xīn dé lì, rú yīng rú yīng zhǎn chì shàng téng
 xiàng shén yǎng liǎn, xiàng shén yǎng liǎn, shēn zhī tā bì yòng xiào liǎn bāng zhù wǒ men.</lyrics>
<title>xiàng shén yǎng liǎn 迦南138</title>
